name: Artifact IV
description: After many sleepless nights alone in the dark, studying the mechanism, you finally discovered its core and managed to remove it from the machinery. But now that it's in your hands, pulsating with a strange light, you can feel the ground started to rumble. Only one question remains. How will you get out of here?
